or Genocide*     <BR>
 
Prusiner  S.B, "The Prion Diseases" Scientific American. Jan 1995<BR>

Richard Lacy,  "How Now Mad Cow", 1995   <BR>
 
Dr. Shaun Heaphy, "Prion Diseases"1996      <BR>
      
