	<td><pre><FONT COLOR="FF00FF">c</FONT>v<FONT COLOR="FF00FF">n</FONT>iti---------kqhtvttt</pre>
	<td><pre>tkge<FONT COLOR="FF00FF">n</FONT>ft</pre>
	<td><pre>etdvkmme-rvv-----eqm<FONT COLOR="FF00FF">c</FONT>itq</pre>
	<td><pre>yeresqayyqrg-</pre>
	<td><pre>ssmvlfsspp---villi-sfliflivg</pre>
</TABLE>
<p><CENTER><IMG  SRC="colorbar_anim.gif" WIDTH="200" HEIGHT="1"></CENTER><p>
<H4>Origin of the Repeat Region</H4>

<PRE>
---------early vertebrate lineage
B O1 H1
B O1 H1 H2 H3

---------chicken lineage
B O1 H1 H2 H3 H4 H5 H6 H7
B O1 H1 H2 H3 H3 H3 H4 H5 H6 H7

-----------marsupial lineage
B O1 H1 H2 H3 O2 O3 O3 O3

-----------mammalian lineage
B O1 H1 H2 H3 H3 H3</PRE>
<p><CENTER><IMG  SRC="colorbar_anim.gif" WIDTH="200" HEIGHT="1"></CENTER><p>

<H4>Helix C in humans begins at boundary of first repeat:</H4>
<PRE> 
_ac cgc tac cc<FONT COLOR="663300">a cct ca</FONT>g ggc ggt ggt
(N)  R   Y   P   P   Q   G   G   G</PRE>
<p><CENTER><IMG  SRC="colorbar_anim.gif" WIDTH="200" HEIGHT="1"></CENTER><p>

